714420f-a.title: Manhattan: 74th Street (East) - 3rd Avenue
714420f-a.text:
East 74th Street, east from but not including Third Avenue. This view
showing prominentlv the north side, depicts a demolition in progress at
No's. 225 to 239 inclusive.
March 29, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
Nlea. aN So5i
